<subSubSection pageId="23" pageNumber="24" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="23.[151,1436,152,498]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,331,431,457]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Etymology</emphasis>
. The specific name comes from the Greek “cerato”, meaning horn, and refers to the hornshaped process from the middle of the valva.
</paragraph>
